title: I Am Ashamed To Be A Human Being...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at AI girlfriends and how to rise of such a product is not designed for self-care but rather as a tool that I believe pushes people to even lonelier ends. Do not waste your time or money with these and instead work on yourself. Thanks for watching!

Check out the newest podcast episode: https://youtu.be/tg7gjHJvxtI
